<hw>firebug</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a criminal who illegally sets fire
to property; an arsonist.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> arsonist, incendiary.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a brightly colored type of true bug that can exude a
